property_headline: Selection of brand new one bedroom apartments for lease
property_description: Nestled in the heart of Sydney's vibrant new hub, The Daniel offers unparalleled living between the bustling growth corridor linking the eastern beaches and the CBD. The Daniel is positioned close to the Gunyama Aquatic Centre, public parks, and transport connections. It offers outstanding lifestyle opportunities with private places to relax, and community places to socialise, exclusive to its residents. Peters Street is access off George Julius Avenue State-of-the-art stainless-steel appliances Stone benchtops complemented by high-end cabinets Expansive living spaces and generously sized bedrooms Hard wearing timber flooring throughout living areas Energy-efficient LED lighting Secure building with video intercom Climate controlled comfort with integrated air conditioning Spectacular rooftop communal spaces boasting panoramic city views EV charging available with selected apartments Custom app offering concierge services at your fingertips Designed to cater to diverse lifestyles, The Daniel offers well-crafted apartments, complemented by access to superior community amenities. Enjoy the convenience of an eight-minute walk to Green Square Station, 20 minutes to the CBD on public transport while Coogee Beach is just a 16-minute drive away.
